Additional Notes for Junior Developer

Focus on performance optimization from the start as WebGL can be demanding
Keep the visual style intentionally simplified to match the meme's aesthetic
Use Three.js's built-in geometries where possible to reduce development time
Consider using a physics library like Cannon.js for more realistic movement, but this is optional for the first version